'''点火孔'''是一个小孔，通过它可点燃[[加农炮|加农炮]]或[[前膛枪|前膛枪]]的推进剂。

將帶刺的鋼釘塞到點火孔裏很難拔出來，這使得大砲無法點火發射。如果大砲有被敵方奪走的危險，我方就會釘塞點火孔，以免敵方用它來砲擊我方。如果我方不能運走擄獲的大砲，也會釘塞點火孔，以免敵方奪回後用來砲擊我方。如果沒有特製的鋼釘可用，也可以將刺刀插到點火孔中，再將其打斷，使刀尖嵌入點火孔。<ref name="Lytle2004">{{cite book|author=Richard M. Lytle|title=The Soldiers of America's First Army, 1791|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UDxBU0JfgjMC&pg=PA101|date=1 January 2004|publisher=Scarecrow Press|isbn=978-0-8108-5011-8|page=101}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=On the Uses and Application of Cavalry in War |last=Bismarck |first=Friedrich Wilhelm |authorlink= |year=1855 |publisher=T and W Boone |location=London |isbn= |page=viii |pages= |accessdate=September 13, 2012 |url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=s28DAAAAYAAJ&printsec=frontcover&source=bl&ots=9Q_qD0JnUs&sig=KG12LU8PB1_YeNXLvRLPva_fGts&hl=en&sa=X&ei=DZRTUJHQMoWzhAf07ICQDA&ved=0CDQQuwUwAA#v=onepage&q&f=false |archive-date=2018-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181117104856/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=s28DAAAAYAAJ&printsec=frontcover&source=bl&ots=9Q_qD0JnUs&sig=KG12LU8PB1_YeNXLvRLPva_fGts&hl=en&sa=X&ei=DZRTUJHQMoWzhAf07ICQDA&ved=0CDQQuwUwAA#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}, translated by [[North_Ludlow_Beamish|North Ludlow Beamish]]</ref>

